:PATH
Chip: Code
Syntax-highlighted code snippets as a first-class chip. Useful for developer \
slates, tutorials, and technical documentation.

:PATH
Discovery Improvements
Better search, tag filtering, and niche-specific pages, making it easier to \
find slates that match a specific interest or use case.

:PATH
AI: Slate Refresh
Update an existing slate's content via AI without starting from scratch. \
Useful for keeping long-lived slates current.

:PATH
Team Slates
Shared slates with multi-contributor access. Multiple authors, one slate, \
with clear ownership and edit controls.

:PATH
Analytics Dashboard
Per-chip engagement metrics for creators. See which chips get the most \
attention and how visitors move through a slate.

:PATH
Internal Messaging
Direct messaging between creators inside the platform. A lightweight \
inbox for collaboration, feedback, and community building.

:PATH
Community Podcast
A recurring show spotlighting authors and their work. Each episode \
features a creator, their slate, and the story behind it.

:PATH
Mobile App
Native iOS and Android slate viewer with offline support, push notifications, \
and a reading experience built for mobile-first audiences.
